{"tid":1535202,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"如何避免被野狗野豬咬住背囊叼走","createTime":"2019-09-03T09:23:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T01:37:51.000Z","uid":199208,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"cd99ac4c412b0b67930f62eb7d41e0af7ea7209b","tid":1535202,"uid":199208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T09:23:57.000Z","msg":"最近發現有好多人行山戈陣比野狗野豬咬住左個背囊, 之後就比牠們拖走再叼入巢<br />\n或者係個背包勾住左棵樹走唔到<br />\n為左解決呢個情況, 小弟不才, 有以下建議供大家參考改進<br />\nSorry如果曾經有人開post講過<br />\n<br />\n我的諗法係唔用背包條帶, 額外自己加條帶, 好似下圖咁<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tmyBqhn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtmyBqhn.jpg&h=e334567e&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n呢條女裝, 如果背包重可以用粗d的帶<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QQQoPKn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQQQoPKn.jpg&h=7fe6ad41&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n然後好似下圖咁扣住下方個扣位, 以小弟著uniqlo s碼的身型將條外置帶拉到最緊, 同背包平時條帶差唔多, 真係唔夠緊, 因為條帶係布黎, 可以縫幾針較緊佢<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JLhZn6f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJLhZn6f.jpg&h=d1c90a13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我知個扣開口細又難開, 危險時未必可以一秒開到<br />\n所以可以加條繩, 一邊用死結綁住背包下面扣位條帶, 一面打一個留有大洞的結, 用黎勾住行山扣, 行山扣另一邊扣住條外置帶的扣, 好似下圖咁 (自行幻想中間有個行山扣, 同埋個結應該要大返幾倍)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eN1SH9P.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeN1SH9P.jpg&h=2ea2cbd2&s={SIZE}\" />  <br />\n如果有人唔知咩係行山扣, 我search左<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wRaL291.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwRaL291.jpg&h=7b9cf347&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咁個洞大左, 行山扣開起黎又方便, 有事可以一秒開左扣棄袋逃走<br />\n<br />\n真係唔想再有人因為個袋而出事了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最近野豬野狗好惡, 大家行山要小心保護自己呀!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90458e199c39d49b506360d0ced718db5131723e","tid":1535202,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T09:24:51.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"336f673e8fc9cf37744f95e19f81fe26b60533e8","tid":1535202,"uid":199208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T09:26:09.000Z","msg":"自推10連"},{"pid":"a2f8064ea9ee8f935e59ef19e85eb75e25a59791","tid":1535202,"uid":199208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T09:26:20.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"2e6f15cb5be615b87229956e0d776cd859d69dc5","tid":1535202,"uid":199208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T09:26:30.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"30218f4482f525833939acd1c1b588068478a780","tid":1535202,"uid":259329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T09:26:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d37069990d84f5dd40f12aa0ac6aef5147221d56","tid":1535202,"uid":199208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T09:26:40.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"e564